                    <span>Great insight of the true heroism that took place inside the towers on 9/11.  The authors do such a great job of humanizing the survivors while honoring those who perished. I feel as if I know the victims of this horrible attack a little better which will allow me to honor them in a more personal way in the years to come. </span>
                  
